    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/e8744b1553c57ac0ecc102f0252ed533.avif?t=1664344638\" width=620 height=86 /></span><br><br><strong>《夜幕降临前(Before The Night)》</strong> 是一款恐怖动作冒险游戏。你将游历可爱动物的世界。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/fa58b864b8a9e70dc15a8ce9b59c5032.avif?t=1664344638\" width=620 height=400 /></span><br><br>成为宠物人“丽萨”，在可爱的动物手中存活下来！ <br><br>加入“丽萨”的旅程，帮助她复活主人！ <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/6650427a3e8df36353f46c16d13d938a.avif?t=1664344638\" width=620 height=318 /></span><br><br>动物村里有珍贵的生命之花。夺走它们所重视的一切，实现复仇吧！ <br><br>兔兔们用各种手段保护着珍贵的生命之花。（比如锁或陷阱之类的东西。） <br><br>要想获得生命之花，要按照不同情况使用道具。 <br><br><br><strong>获得道具的方法 1. 物物交换。 </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/45e35d8afa59a8dac9ae9ba14c7536e8.avif?t=1664344638\" width=620 height=318 /></span><br><br>给兔兔新鲜的胡萝卜，获得钥匙或武器！ <br><br>兔兔们对胡萝卜欲罢不能！ <br><br><br><strong>获得道具的方法 2. 锤子 </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/578001a421b17b64967a11ae0cd11aba.poster.avif?t=1664344638\" width=512 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/578001a421b17b64967a11ae0cd11aba.webm?t=1664344638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/578001a421b17b64967a11ae0cd11aba.mp4?t=1664344638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>村里的居民们不配合吗？锤子是很好的对话手段！ <br><br>请使用各种武器与动物进行物理对话！ <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/6030c39fded3403e347cfbb9cb1d06db.avif?t=1664344638\" width=620 height=86 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/a329b8a6b437f6218751cbf9c78d4bff.poster.avif?t=1664344638\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/a329b8a6b437f6218751cbf9c78d4bff.webm?t=1664344638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/a329b8a6b437f6218751cbf9c78d4bff.mp4?t=1664344638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>“快跑！！！”</strong><br><br>摘下生命之花，就会使村庄陷入黑暗！ <br><br>被黑暗污染的兔兔居民们会变成怪物！ <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/c799dc373f42a1d41a52aaf094a03287.poster.avif?t=1664344638\" width=512 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/c799dc373f42a1d41a52aaf094a03287.webm?t=1664344638\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/c799dc373f42a1d41a52aaf094a03287.mp4?t=1664344638\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在充满紧张感的追击战中生存下来吧！ <br><br>躲在草丛里，或用食物引诱怪物！ <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829420/extras/069eb2efdd0e6861747790f0630880c5.avif?t=1664344638\" width=620 height=360 /></span><br><br>在<strong>《夜幕降临前(Before The Night)》</strong>的世界里，与各种各样的动物朋友们一起生存下去吧！<br><br><strong>游戏特色 </strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">【*遇见一到夜晚就会变成怪物的可爱动物朋友。】</ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">【*聆听宠物人的感动故事。】 </ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">【*试着将可爱的NPC制作成肉。】 </ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">【*给兔兔胡萝卜并获得锤子。】 </ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">【*用锤子捕猎兔兔。】 </ul><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">【*和可爱的动物村民们一起愉快地玩捉迷藏。】 </ul>",
